Saved!
Job Details
A Security & IT Systems Integrator company is looking for a highly energetic & organized Sales Co-coordinator to systematically manage the pre-sales and post sales operations. The responsibilities are as follows:1. Understand the product range/solutions.2. Liaise with the projects / sales team to understand the Bill of Material requirements.3. Prepare the quotes4. Follow up on the quotes with the clients.5. On finalization , prepare LPO & liaise with the suppliers for deliveries.6. Maintain /manage all the necessary documentation required.7. Prepare & handover documents such as drawings, certificates etc.8. Maintain stock information.Female applicants only.Qualification : Electronics Engineer
